  <name>Decrediton</name>
  <summary>Decred cryptocurrency wallet</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Decrediton is the official cross-platform GUI wallet for Decred (DCR),
      built with Electron. It provides full wallet functionality, from sending
      and receiving funds to participating in Decred's Proof-of-Stake system and
      on-chain governance.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Send and receive DCR</li>
      <li>SPV (light) mode for fast setup without a full blockchain download</li>
      <li>Purchase tickets for Proof-of-Stake voting</li>
      <li>Manage multiple wallets and accounts</li>
      <li>View and export transaction history</li>
      <li>Integrated Politeia and consensus-rule governance voting</li>
      <li>Built-in privacy mixing (StakeShuffle / CoinShuffle++)</li>
      <li>Optional Trezor hardware wallet support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

